title: O'Neill Girls Surftrip to Bali with Eva Kreyer (GE) and Lisa veith(AT)
description:
O'Neill Girls from Germany (Eva Kreyer -- Surf) & Austria (Lisa Veith -- Surf & Skate) travelled to Bali to discover the beautiful island. There are still places to explore and the girls show you the feeling and spirit of this wonderful island. Lean back, turn on the loudspeaker and enjoy their surf trip to Bali.

"Special thanks & much love to Simon Huber (Filmer) & Lars Jacobsen (Photographer) & our teamriders Eva Kreyer and Lisa Veith"

"Also a huge THANK YOU to the KIMASURF Crew on Bali"
